                <div class=\"motive-header\">\n                            <div class=\"motive-icon\">\n                                <i class=\"fas fa-coins\"></i>\n                            </div>\n                            <div class=\"motive-title\">财政系统崩溃</div>\n                        </div>\n                        <div class=\"motive-content\">\n                            冗官、冗兵、对外战争消耗导致国库空虚，税负转嫁激化矛盾\n                        </div>\n                        <div class=\"motive-tag\">系统性危机</div>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"motive-card\">\n                        <div class=\"motive-header\">\n                            <div class=\"motive-icon\">\n                                <i class=\"fas fa-users\"></i>\n                            </div>\n                            <div class=\"motive-title\">人口资源失衡</div>\n                        </div>\n                        <div class=\"motive-content\">\n                            人口压力与资源环境承载极限（马尔萨斯陷阱），生存危机蔓延\n                        </div>\n                        <div class=\"motive-tag\">生态压力</div>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"motive-card\">\n                        <div class=\"motive-header\">\n                            <div class=\"motive-icon\">\n                                <i class=\"fas fa-layer-group\"></i>\n                            </div>\n                            <div class=\"motive-title\">社会结构固化</div>\n                        </div>\n                        <div class=\"motive-content\">\n                            严重的阶级固化与社会流动性停滞，底层上升通道完全封闭\n                        </div>\n                        <div class=\"motive-tag\">流动性丧失</div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            <!-- 底部因果链摘要 -->\n            <div class=\"causal-chain\">\n                <div class=\"chain-item\">土地兼并</div>\n                <div class=\"chain-arrow\">→</div>\n                <div class=\"chain-item\">自耕农破产</div>\n                <div class=\"chain-arrow\">→</div>\n                <div class=\"chain-item\">税基萎缩</div>\n                <div class=\"chain-arrow\">→</div>\n                <div class=\"chain-item\">财政危机</div>\n                <div class=\"chain-arrow\">→</div>\n                <div class=\"chain-item\">加征赋税</div>\n                <div class=\"chain-arrow\">→</div>\n                <div class=\"chain-item chain-highlight\">农民起义</div>\n                <div class=\"chain-arrow\">→</div>\n                <div class=\"chain-item chain-highlight\">王朝崩溃</div>\n            </div>\n        </main>\n        <!-- 底部页码栏 -->\n        <footer class=\"footer\">\n            <div class=\"footer-left\">\n                <i class=\"fas fa-landmark icon\"></i> 王朝更替的历史逻辑与模式分析\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"footer-right\">\n                <div class=\"page-numbers\">\n                    <span class=\"current-page\">6</span> / <span class=\"total-pages\">12</span>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"footer-icons\">\n                    <i class=\"fas fa-scroll icon\"></i>\n                    <i class=\"fas fa-history icon\"></i>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </footer>\n    </div>\n    <!-- ECharts 桑基图脚本 -->\n    <script>\n        const chartDom = document.getElementById(\'sankey-chart\');\n        const myChart = echarts.init(chartDom);\n        const sankeyData = {\n            nodes: [\n                {','{}',NULL,0,1773390000,1773390000),(34,'925b3736-a913-4202-bb87-8fc5d3443390',6,'slide_6','四、模式归纳：周期律、断裂与连续','content','<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"zh-CN\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>四、模式归纳：周期律、断裂与连续 - 中国王朝更替历史</title>\n    <!-- Font Awesome 图标 -->\n    <link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css\">\n    <!-- 谷歌字体：思源宋体 & 思源黑体 -->\n    <li