cube\"></i>\n                            概念与原理\n                        </div>\n                        <div class=\"concept-list\">\n                            <div class=\"concept-item\">\n                                <div class=\"concept-icon\">1</div>\n                                <div class=\"concept-text\">\n                                    <h4>二级指针 (int **pp)</h4>\n                                    <p>指向指针的指针，存储的是指针变量的地址</p>\n                                    <div class=\"code-example\">\n                                        int a = 10;<br>\n                                        int *p = &a;    // p指向a<br>\n                                        int **pp = &p;  // pp指向p\n                                    </div>\n                                </div>\n                            </div>\n                            <div class=\"concept-item\">\n                                <div class=\"concept-icon\">2</div>\n                                <div class=\"concept-text\">\n                                    <h4>声明与初始化</h4>\n                                    <p>多级指针的声明语法与层级对应关系</p>\n                                    <div class=\"code-example\">\n                                        int **pp;<br><br>\n                                        int ***ppp;<br><br>\n                                        int x = 5;<br>\n                                        int *p = &x;<br>\n                                        int **pp = &p;\n                                    </div>\n                                </div>\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"memory-diagram\">\n                        <div class=\"diagram-title\">\n                            <i class=\"fas fa-sitemap\"></i>\n                            内存层级图解\n                        </div>\n                        <div class=\"diagram-container\">\n                            <div class=\"pointer-levels\">\n                                <div class=\"level-box level-3\">\n                                    <div class=\"level-label\">三级指针</div>\n                                    <div class=\"level-value\">ppp</div>\n                                    <div class=\"level-address\">0x1008</div>\n                                </div>\n                                <div class=\"arrow\">→</div>\n                                <div class=\"level-box level-2\">\n                                    <div class=\"level-label\">二级指针</div>\n                                    <div class=\"level-value\">pp</div>\n                                    <div class=\"level-address\">0x1010</div>\n                                </div>\n                                <div class=\"arrow\">→</div>\n                                <div class=\"level-box level-1\">\n                                    <div class=\"level-label\">一级指针</div>\n                                    <div class=\"level-value\">p</div>\n                                    <div class=\"level-address\">0x1018</div>\n                                </div>\n                                <div class=\"arrow\">→</div>\n                                <div class=\"level-box\" style=\"background:linear-gradient(135deg, #fce4ec, #f8bbd9); border:3px solid #f48fb1;\">\n                                    <div class=\"level-label\">整型变量</div>\n                                    <div class=\"level-value\">a = 10</div>\n                                    <div class=\"level-address\">0x1020</div>\n                                </div>\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <!-- 右侧面板：应用与实践 -->\n                <div class=\"right-panel\">\n                    <div class=\"application-card\">\n                        <div','{}',NULL,0,1773720000,1773720000),(56,'d2191990-b108-4b42-8218-35c46b7c4b86',4,'slide_4','动态内存管理：malloc与free','content','<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"zh-CN\">\n<head>\n<meta charset=\"UTF-8\" />\n<meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\" />\n<title>动态内存管理：malloc与free</title>\n<link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css\">\n<link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/prism/1.29.0/themes/prism-tomorrow.min.css\">\n<script src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/chart.js\"></script>\n<script src=\"https://polyfill.io/v3/polyfill.min.js?features=es6\"></script>\n<script id=\"MathJax-script\" async src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/mathjax@3/es5/tex-mml-chtml.js\"></script>\n<script src=\"https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/prism/1.29.0/prism.min.js\"></script>\n<script src=\"https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/prism/1.29.0/components/prism-c.min.js\"></script>\n<style>\n    * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }\n    html, body {\n        width: 100%;\n        height: 100%;\n        overflow: hidden;\n        background: #edf1eb;\n        font-family: \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"PingFang SC\", \"Noto Sans SC\", sans-serif;\n        color: #335239;\n    }\n    .slide-container {\n        width: 100vw;\n        height: 100vh;\n        display: flex;\n        align-items: center;\n        justify-content: center;\n    }\n    .slide {\n        width: 1280px;\n        height: 720px;\n        position: relative;\n        overflow: hidden;\n        transform-origin: center center;\n        border-radius: 16px;\n        background: linear-gradient(180deg, #f8faf6 0%, #f2f5ef 100%);\n        box-shadow: 0 18px 42px rgba(0,0,0,.14);\n    }\n    /* 页眉 - 严格保持原样 */\n    .header {\n        position: absolute;\n        left: 30px;\n        right: 30px;\n        top: 24px;\n        display: grid;\n        grid-template-columns: 1fr auto;\n        gap: 20px;\n        align-items: start;\n        z-index: 30;\n    }\n    .header h1 {\n        font-size: 28px;\n        line-height: 1.2;\n        color: #48724a;\n        font-weight: 900;\n        letter-spacing: .4px;\n    }\n    .header p {\n        margin-top: 7px;\n        font-size: 12px;\n        color: #7e8e7f;\n        line-height: 1.55;\n        max-width: 650px;\n    }\n    .main-tabs {\n        display: flex;\n        gap: 10px;\n        align-items: center;\n        flex-wrap: wrap;\n        justify-content: flex-end;\n    }\n    .main-tab {\n        border: 1px solid rgba(90,121,80,.18);\n        background: rgba(255,255,255,.92);\n        color: #5f7860;\n        border-radius: 999px;\n        padding: 9px 16px;\n        font-size: 14px;\n        font-weight: 800;\n        cursor: pointer;\n        transition: all .18s ease;\n    }\n    .main-tab.active {\n        background: #4e7b47;\n        color: #fff;\n        box-shadow: 0 8px 18px rgba(78,123,71,.28);\n    }\n    /* 主要内容区域 - 创意设计部分 */\n    .content-area {\n        position: absolute;\n        left: 28px;\n        right: 28px;\n        top: 98px;\n        bottom: 26px;\n        display: flex;\n        flex-direction: column;\n        gap: 16px;\n    }\n    .page-title {\n        color: #4a7b43;\n        font-size: 32px;\n        font-weight: 900;\n        margin-bottom: 8px;\n        padding-left: 8px;\n        border-left: 6px solid #7da965;\n    }\n    .content-grid {\n        flex: 1;\n        display: grid;\n        grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;\n        gap: 20px;\n        height: calc(100% - 60px);\n    }\n    .left-column {\n        display: flex;\n        flex-direction: column;\n        gap: 20px;\n    }\n    .right-column {\n        display: flex;\n        flex-direction: column;\n        gap: 20px;\n    }\n    .content-card {\n        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);\n        border-radius: 20px;\n        border: 1px solid rgba(87, 124, 79, 0.15);\n        padding: 22px;\n        box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(78, 123, 71, 0.08);\n        transition: transform 0.3s ease;\n        height: 100%;\n        display: flex;\n        flex-direction: column;\n    }\n    .content-card:hover {\n        transform: translateY(-4px);\n        box-shadow: 0 12px 28px rgba(78, 123, 71, 0.12);\n    }\n    .card-header {\n        display: flex;\n        align-items: center;\n        gap: 12px;\n        margin-bottom: 16px;\n        padding-bottom: 12px;\n        border-bottom: 2px solid #e8f0e4;\n    }\n    .card-icon {\n        width: 42px;\n        height: 42px;\n        border-radius: 12px;\n        display: flex;\n        align-items: center;\n        justify-content: center;\n        font-size: 20px;\n        color: white;\n    }\n    .icon-why { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #4e874c, #6ba068); }\n    .icon-malloc { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #3f6e48, #5a8b54); }\n    .icon-free { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #78a06f, #9ab48e); }\n    .icon-example { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #c9d97c, #dbead3); }\n    .card-title {\n        font-size: 20px;\n        font-weight: 900;\n        color: #48724a;\n        flex: 1;\n    }\n    .card-content {\n        flex: 1;\n        font-size: 15px;\n        line-height: 1.6;\n        color: #5a7a55;\n    }\n    .card-content ul {\n        list-style: none;\n        padding-left: 0;\n    }\n    .card-content li {\n        margin-bottom: 10px;\n        padding-left: 24px;\n        position: relative;\n    }\n    .card-content li:before {\n        content: \"•\";\n        position: absolute;\n        left: 0;\n        color: #7da965;\n        font-size: 20px;\n    }\n    .memory-visualization {\n        display: flex;\n        align-items: center;\n        justify-content: space-between;\n        margin-top: 15px;\n        padding: 15px;\n        background: #f8fbf6;\n        border-radius: 12px;\n        border: 1px dashed #c6d6bf;\n    }\n    .memory-block {\n        width: 70px;\n        height: 70px;\n        border-radius: 10px;\n        display: flex;\n        align-items: center;\n        justify-content: center;\n        font-weight: 900;\n        font-size: 14px;\n        color: white;\n        transition: all 0.5s ease;\n        position: relative;\n    }\n    .static-memory {\n        background: #a8b8a8;\n        box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(168, 184, 168, 0.3);\n    }\n    .dynamic-memory {\n        background: #4e874c;\n        box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(78, 135, 76, 0.4);\n    }\n    .memory-label {\n        font-size: 12px;\n        color: #7e8e7f;\n        text-align: center;\n        margin-top: 8px;\n    }\n    .arrow {\n        font-size: 24px;\n        color: #7da965;\n        margin: 0 10px;\n    }\n    .code-container {\n        background: #2d2d2d;\n        border-radius: 12px;\n        overflow: hidden;\n        margin-top: 15px;\n        flex: 1;\n    }\n    .code-header {\n        background: #3c3c3c;\n        padding: 10px 15px;\n        display: flex;\n        justify-content: space-between;\n        align-items: center;\n    }\n    .code-title {\n        color: #e0e0e0;\n        font-size: 14px;\n        font-weight: 600;\n    }\n    .code-copy {\n        color: #7da965;\n        font-size: 12px;\n        cursor: pointer;\n    }\n    .code-content {\n        padding: 15px;\n        font-family: \'Consolas\', \'Monaco\', monospace;\n        font-size: 14px;\n        line-height: 1.5;\n        color: #f8f8f2;\n        overflow: auto;\n        max-height: 200px;\n    }\n    .warning-box {\n        background: #fff8e6;\n        border-left: 5px solid #ffb74d;\n        padding: 15px;\n        border-radius: 8px;\n        margin-top: 15px;\n    }\n    .warning-title {\n        color: #ff9800;\n        font-weight: 900;\n        font-size: 16px;\n        margin-bottom: 8px;\n        display: flex;\n        align-items: center;\n        gap: 8px;\n    }\n    .warning-content {\n        color: #8a6d3b;\n        font-size: 14px;\n        line-height: 1.5;\n    }\n    .function-demo {\n        display: flex;\n        align-items: center;\n        justify-content: space-around;\n        margin-top: 15px;\n        padding: 15px;\n        background: #f0f7ed;\n        border-radius: 12px;\n    }\n    .func-card {\n        display: flex;\n        flex-direction: column;\n        align-items: center;\n        text-align: center;\n        width: 45%;\n    }\n    .func-icon {\n        width: 60px;\n        height: 60px;\n        border-radius: 50%;\n        display: flex;\n        align-items: center;\n        justify-content: center;\n        font-size: 24px;\n        color: white;\n        margin-bottom: 10px;\n    }\n    .malloc-icon { background: #4e874c; }\n    .free-icon { background: #c9d97c; color: #5a7a55; }\n    .func-name {\n        font-weight: 900;\n        font-size: 18px;\n        color: #48724a;\n        margin-bottom: 5px;\n    }\n    .func-desc {\n        font-size: 13px;\n        color: #7e8e7f;\n        line-height: 1.4;\n    }\n    .pair-arrow {\n        font-size: 28px;\n        color: #7da965;\n        margin: 0 10px;\n    }\n    .lifecycle-chart {\n        flex: 1;\n        display: flex;\n        align-items: center;\n        justify-content: center;\n        margin-top: 15px;\n    }\n    .lifecycle-steps {\n        display: flex;\n        align-items: center;\n        justify-content: space-between;\n        width: 100%;\n    }\n    .step {\n        display: flex;\n        flex-direction: column;\n        align-items: center;\n        text-align: center;\n        width: 30%;\n    }\n    .step-circle {\n        width: 70px;\n        height: 70px;\n        border-radius: 50%;\n        display: flex;\n        align-items: center;\n        justify-content: center;\n        font-size: 24px;\n        color: white;\n        margin-bottom: 10px;\n        box-shadow: 0 6px 12px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n    }\n    .step-1 { background: #4e874c; }\n    .step-2 { background: #78a06f; }\n    .step-3 { background: #c9d97c; color: #5a7a55; }\n    .step-label {\n        font-weight: 700;\n        color: #48724a;\n        font-size: 15px;\n    }\n    .step-desc {\n        font-size: 12px;\n        color: #7e8e7f;\n        margin-top: 5px;\n    }\n    .step-arrow {\n        font-size: 24px;\n        color: #7da965;\n        margin: 0 5px;\n    }\n    /* 页脚 - 严格保持原样 */\n    .footer {\n        position: absolute;\n        left: 30px;\n        right: 30px;\n        bottom: 24px;\n        display: flex;\n        justify-content: space-between;\n        align-items: center;\n        z-index: 30;\n    }\n    .footer-left {\n        font-size: 12px;\n        color: #7e8e7f;\n    }\n    .footer-right {\n        font-size: 14px;\n        color: #5f7860;\n        font-weight: 700;\n    }\n    .page-number {\n        background: rgba(255,255,255,.92);\n        border: 1px solid rgba(90,121,80,.18);\n        border-radius: 999px;\n        padding: 6px 14px;\n    }\n    /* 装饰元素 */\n    .decoration {\n        position: absolute;\n        z-index: 1;\n    }\n    .decoration-1 {\n        width: 120px;\n        height: 120px;\n        background: rgba(126, 174, 101, 0.08);\n        border-radius: 50%;\n        top: 120px;\n        right: 80px;\n    }\n    .decoration-2 {\n        width: 80px;\n        height: 80px;\n        background: rgba(201, 217, 124, 0.1);\n        border-radius: 50%;\n        bottom: 100px;\n        left: 100px;\n    }\n    .decoration-3 {\n        width: 60px;\n        height: 60px;\n        background: rgba(78, 135, 76, 0.05);\n        border-radius: 50%;\n        top: 200px;\n        left: 150px;\n    }\n    /* 响应式调整 */\n    @media (max-width: 1350px) {\n        .content-grid {\n            gap: 15px;\n        }\n        .card-content {\n            font-size: 14px;\n        }\n        .card-title {\n            font-size: 18px;\n        }\n    }\n</style>\n</head>\n<body>\n<div class=\"slide-container\">\n    <div class=\"slide\">\n        <!-- 页眉 - 严格保持原样 -->\n        <div class=\"header\">\n            <div>\n                <h1>食品药品职业学院 PPT 模板描述文件（字段规范版）</h1>\n                <p>参照 template.html 的\"单文件、自包含、固定 1280×720、响应式缩放、占位符与规则说明\"写法，在 v3 的子版式拆分基础上，继续把字段命名、选型规则、禁用场景和母版约束标准化，方便后续直接拿来生成新的 PPT。</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"main-tabs\">\n                <button class=\"main-tab\">封面系统</button>\n                <button class=\"main-tab\">目录系统</button>\n                <button class=\"main-tab active\">内容系统</button>\n                <button class=\"main-tab\">数据系统</button>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n        <!-- 装饰元素 -->\n        <div class=\"decoration decoration-1\"></div>\n        <div class=\"decoration decoration-2\"></div>\n        <div class=\"decoration decoration-3\"></div>\n        <!-- 主要内容区域 - 创意设计部分 -->\n        <div class=\"content-area\">\n            <div class=\"page-title\">动态内存管理：malloc与free</div>\n            <div class=\"content-grid\">\n                <!-- 左列 -->\n                <div class=\"left-column\">\n                    <!-- 为什么需要动态内存分配？ -->\n                    <div class=\"content-card\">\n                        <div class=\"card-header\">\n                            <div class=\"card-icon icon-why\">\n                                <i class=\"fas fa-question-circle\"></i>\n                            </div>\n                            <div class=\"card-title\">为什么需要动态内存分配？</div>\n                        </div>\n                        <div class=\"card-content\">\n                            <ul>\n                                <li>静态内存分配在编译时确定大小，无法适应运行时需求变化</li>\n                                <li>动态内存允许程序在运行时申请所需内存，提高灵活性</li>\n                                <li>适用于数据结构大小未知或变化的情况</li>\n                            </ul>\n                            <div class=\"memory-visualization\">\n                                <div>\n                                    <div class=\"memory-block static-memory\">固定</div>\n                                    <div class=\"memory-label\">静态分配</div>\n                                </div>\n                                <div class=\"arrow\"><i class=\"fas fa-arrow-right\"></i></div>\n                                <div>\n                                    <div class=\"memory-block dynamic-memory\">灵活</div>\n                                    <div class=\"memory-label\">动态分配</div>\n                                </div>\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <!-- malloc函数：申请指定字节数的内存 -->\n                    <div class=\"content-card\">\n                        <div class=\"card-header\">\n                            <div class=\"card-icon icon-malloc\">\n                                <i class=\"fas fa-plus-circle\"></i>\n                            </div>\n                            <div class=\"card-title\">malloc函数：申请内存</div>\n                        </div>\n                        <div class=\"card-content\">\n                            <p','{}',NULL,0,1773720000,1773720000),(57,'d2191990-b108-4b42-8218-35c46b7c4b86',5,'slide_5','动态内存管理：calloc与realloc','content','<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"zh-CN\">\n<head>\n<meta charset=\"UTF-8\" />\n<meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\" />\n<title>动态内存管理：calloc与realloc</title>\n<link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css\">\n<link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/prism/1.29.0/themes/prism-tomorrow.min.css\">\n<script src=\"https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/prism/1.29.0/prism.min.js\"></script>\n<script src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/chart.js\"></script>\n<style>\n    * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }\n    html, body {\n        width: 100%;\n        height: 100%;\n        overflow: hidden;\n        background: #edf1eb;\n        font-family: \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"PingFang SC\", \"Noto Sans SC\", sans-serif;\n        color: #335239;\n    }\n    .slide-container {\n        width: 100vw;\n        height: 100vh;\n        display: flex;\n        align-items: center;\n        justify-content: center;\n    }\n    .slide {\n        width: 1280px;\n        height: 720px;\n        position: relative;\n        overflow: hidden;\n        transform-origin: center center;\n        border-radius: 16px;\n        background: linear-gradient(180deg, #f8faf6 0%, #f2f5ef 100%);\n        box-shadow: 0 18px 42px rgba(0,0,0,.14);\n    }\n    /* 页眉 - 严格保持原样 */\n    .header {\n        position: absolute;\n        left: 30px;\n        right: 30px;\n        top: 24px;\n        display: grid;\n        grid-template-columns: 1fr auto;\n        gap: 20px;\n        align-items: start;\n        z-index: 30;\n    }\n    .header h1 {\n        font-size: 28px;\n        line-height: 1.2;\n        color: #48724a;\n        font-weight: 900;\n        letter-spacing: .4px;\n    }\n    .header p {\n        margin-top: 7px;\n        font-size: 12px;\n        color: #7e8e7f;\n        line-height: 1.55;\n        max-width: 650px;\n    }\n    .main-tabs {\n        display: flex;\n        gap: 10px;\n        align-items: center;\n        flex-wrap: wrap;\n        justify-content: flex-end;\n    }\n    .main-tab {\n        border: 1px solid rgba(90,121,80,.18);\n        background: rgba(255,255,255,.92);\n        color: #5f7860;\n        border-radius: 999px;\n        padding: 9px 16px;\n        font-size: 14px;\n        font-weight: 800;\n        cursor: pointer;\n        transition: all .18s ease;\n    }\n    .main-tab.active {\n        background: #4e7b47;\n        color: #fff;\n        box-shadow: 0 8px 18px rgba(78,123,71,.28);\n    }\n    /* 主要内容区域 - 创意设计部分 */\n    .content-area {\n        position: absolute;\n        left: 30px;\n        right: 30px;\n        top: 98px;\n        bottom: 60px;\n        display: flex;\n        flex-direction: column;\n        gap: 20px;\n    }\n    .page-title {\n        color: #4e7b47;\n        font-size: 32px;\n        font-weight: 900;\n        text-align: center;\n        margin-bottom: 10px;\n        position: relative;\n        padding-bottom: 12px;\n    }\n    .page-title::after {\n        content: \'\';\n        position: absolute;\n        bottom: 0;\n        left: 50%;\n        transform: translateX(-50%);\n        width: 120px;\n        height: 4px;\n        background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, #7da965, transparent);\n        border-radius: 2px;\n    }\n    .main-content {\n        flex: 1;\n        display: grid;\n        grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;\n        gap: 24px;\n        height: calc(100% - 60px);\n    }\n    .function-card {\n        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);\n        border-radius: 20px;\n        padding: 24px;\n        box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(78, 123, 71, 0.08);\n        border: 1px solid rgba(87, 124, 79, 0.15);\n        display: flex;\n        flex-direction: column;\n        transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;\n    }\n    .function-card:hover {\n        transform: translateY(-5px);\n        box-shadow: 0 15px 40px rgba(78, 123, 71, 0.15);\n    }\n    .card-header {\n        display: flex;\n        align-items: center;\n        margin-bottom: 20px;\n        padding-bottom: 15px;\n        border-bottom: 2px solid #e8f0e5;\n    }\n    .function-icon {\n        width: 60px;\n        height: 60px;\n        border-radius: 50%;\n        display: flex;\n        align-items: center;\n        justify-content: center;\n        margin-right: 18px;\n        font-size: 24px;\n        color: white;\n        flex-shrink: 0;\n    }\n    .calloc-icon {\n        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1abc9c, #16a085);\n    }\n    .realloc-icon {\n        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f39c12, #e67e22);\n    }\n    .function-title {\n        font-size: 24px;\n        font-weight: 900;\n        color: #2c3e50;\n        margin-bottom: 5px;\n    }\n    .function-subtitle {\n        font-size: 14px;\n        color: #7f8c8d;\n        font-weight: 500;\n    }\n    .function-details {\n        flex: 1;\n        display: flex;\n        flex-direction: column;\n        gap: 16px;\n    }\n    .detail-item {\n        display: flex;\n        align-items: flex-start;\n        margin-bottom: 8px;\n    }\n    .detail-label {\n        font-weight: 700;\n        color: #48724a;\n        min-width: 80px;\n        font-size: 15px;\n    }\n    .detail-content {\n        flex: 1;\n        color: #335239;\n        line-height: 1.5;\n        font-size: 15px;\n    }\n    .code-block {\n        background: #2c3e50;\n        border-radius: 12px;\n        padding: 16px;\n        margin-top: 10px;\n        overflow-x: auto;\n    }\n    .code-block pre {\n        margin: 0;\n        font-family: \'Consolas\', \'Monaco\', monospace;\n        font-size: 14px;\n        color: #ecf0f1;\n        line-height: 1.4;\n    }\n    .memory-visualization {\n        height: 120px;\n        background: #f8f9fa;\n        border-radius: 12px;\n        margin-top: 15px;\n        padding: 12px;\n        border: 1px dashed #bdc3c7;\n        display: flex;\n        align-items: center;\n        justify-content: center;\n        position: relative;\n    }\n    .memory-block {\n        width: 40px;\n        height: 40px;\n        border-radius: 6px;\n        margin: 0 5px;\n        display: flex;\n        align-items: center;\n        justify-content: center;\n        font-weight: 700;\n        font-size: 12px;\n        color: white;\n        transition: all 0.3s ease;\n    }\n    .memory-block.zero {\n        background: #1abc9c;\n    }\n    .memory-block.data {\n        background: #3498db;\n    }\n    .memory-block.new {\n        background: #f39c12;\n    }\n    .memory-block.uninit {\n        background: #bdc3c7;\n        color: #7f8c8d;\n    }\n    .comparison-section {\n        grid-column: 1 / span 2;\n        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95);\n        border-radius: 20px;\n        padding: 24px;\n        margin-top: 10px;\n        box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(78, 123, 71, 0.08);\n        border: 1px solid rgba(87, 124, 79, 0.15);\n    }\n    .section-title {\n        font-size: 22px;\n        font-weight: 900;\n        color: #4e7b47;\n        margin-bottom: 20px;\n        display: flex;\n        align-items: center;\n    }\n    .section-title i {\n        margin-right: 10px;\n        color: #7da965;\n    }\n    .comparison-table {\n        width: 100%;\n        border-collapse: collapse;\n        margin-top: 10px;\n    }\n    .comparison-table th {\n        background: #f1f8e9;\n        color: #48724a;\n        font-weight: 900;\n        padding: 16px 12px;\n        text-align: center;\n        border-bottom: 2px solid #c8e6c9;\n        font-size: 16px;\n    }\n    .comparison-table td {\n        padding: 14px 12px;\n        text-align: center;\n        border-bottom: 1px solid #e8f5e8;\n        color: #335239;\n        font-size: 15px;\n    }\n    .comparison-table tr:last-child td {\n        border-bottom: none;\n    }\n    .comparison-table tr:hover {\n        background: #f9fdf9;\n    }\n    .highlight-cell {\n        background: #e8f5e8;\n        font-weight: 700;\n        color: #2e7d32;\n    }\n    .error-handling {\n        grid-column: 1 / span 2;\n        background: rgba(253, 237, 236, 0.9);\n        border-radius: 20px;\n        padding: 22px;\n        margin-top: 10px;\n        border-left: 6px solid #e74c3c;\n        box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(231, 76, 60, 0.1);\n    }\n    .error-title {\n        font-size: 20px;\n        font-weight: 900;\n        color: #c0392b;\n        margin-bottom: 15px;\n        display: flex;\n        align-items: center;\n    }\n    .error-title i {\n        margin-right: 10px;\n    }\n    .error-steps {\n        display: grid;\n        grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);\n        gap: 16px;\n        margin-top: 10px;\n    }\n    .error-step {\n        background: white;\n        border-radius: 12px;\n        padding: 16px;\n        text-align: center;\n        box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);\n        transition: transform 0.3s ease;\n    }\n    .error-step:hover {\n        transform: translateY(-5px);\n    }\n    .step-number {\n        width: 36px;\n        height: 36px;\n        background: #e74c3c;\n        color: white;\n        border-radius: 50%;\n        display: flex;\n        align-items: center;\n        justify-content: center;\n        font-weight: 900;\n        margin: 0 auto 12px;\n        font-size: 18px;\n    }\n    .step-title {\n        font-weight: 700;\n        color: #c0392b;\n        margin-bottom: 8px;\n        font-size: 16px;\n    }\n    .step-desc {\n        color: #7f8c8d;\n        font-size: 14px;\n        line-height: 1.4;\n    }\n    /* 页脚 - 严格保持原样 */\n    .footer {\n        position: absolute;\n        left: 30px;\n        right: 30px;\n        bottom: 20px;\n        display: flex;\n        justify-content: space-between;\n        align-items: center;\n        z-index: 30;\n    }\n    .footer .page-number {\n        font-size: 14px;\n        color: #7e8e7f;\n        font-weight: 700;\n    }\n    .footer .decorative-line {\n        flex: 1;\n        height: 1px;\n        background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, rgba(90,121,80,.2), transparent);\n        margin: 0 20px;\n    }\n    .footer .slide-type {\n        font-size: 12px;\n        color: #7e8e7f;\n        text-transform: uppercase;\n        letter-spacing: 1px;\n    }\n    /* 装饰元素 */\n    .decoration {\n        position: absolute;\n        z-index: 1;\n    }\n    .decoration.circle-1 {\n        width: 120px;\n        height: 120px;\n        border-radius: 50%;\n        background: rgba(141, 198, 63, 0.1);\n        top: 120px;\n        right: 80px;\n    }\n    .decoration.circle-2 {\n        width: 80px;\n        height: 80px;\n        border-radius: 50%;\n        background: rgba(77, 175, 124, 0.08);\n        bottom: 150px;\n        left: 60px;\n    }\n    .decoration.circle-3 {\n        width: 60px;\n        height: 60px;\n        border-radius: 50%;\n        background: rgba(52, 152, 219, 0.05);\n        top: 200px;\n        left: 100px;\n    }\n    /* 响应式调整 */\n    @media (max-width: 1350px) {\n        .slide {\n            transform: scale(0.9);\n        }\n    }\n</style>\n</head>\n<body>\n<div class=\"slide-container\">\n    <div class=\"slide\">\n        <!-- 页眉 - 严格保持原样 -->\n        <div class=\"header\">\n            <div>\n                <h1>食品药品职业学院 PPT 模板描述文件（字段规范版）</h1>\n                <p>参照 template.html 的\"单文件、自包含、固定 1280×720、响应式缩放、占位符与规则说明\"写法，在 v3 的子版式拆分基础上，继续把字段命名、选型规则、禁用场景和母版约束标准化，方便后续直接拿来生成新的 PPT。</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"main-tabs\">\n                <button class=\"main-tab\">封面系统</button>\n                <button class=\"main-tab\">目录系统</button>\n                <button class=\"main-tab active\">内容系统</button>\n                <button class=\"main-tab\">数据系统</button>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n        <!-- 主要内容区域 - 创意设计部分 -->\n        <div class=\"content-area\">\n            <h2 class=\"page-title\">动态内存管理：calloc与realloc</h2>\n            <div class=\"main-content\">\n                <!-- Calloc 函数卡片 -->\n                <div class=\"function-card\">\n                    <div class=\"card-header\">\n                        <div class=\"function-icon calloc-icon\">\n                            <i class=\"fas fa-layer-group\"></i>\n                        </div>\n                        <div>\n                            <h3 class=\"function-title\">calloc 函数</h3>\n                            <p class=\"function-subtitle\">分配并初始化为零</p>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"function-details\">\n                        <div class=\"detail-item\">\n                            <span class=\"detail-label\">功能：</span>\n                            <span class=\"detail-content\">分配连续内存块，并将所有位初始化为零</span>\n                        </div>\n                        <div class=\"detail-item\">\n                            <span class=\"detail-label\">语法：</span>\n                            <span class=\"detail-content\">void *calloc(size_t num, size_t size);</span>\n                        </div>\n                        <div class=\"detail-item\">\n                            <span class=\"detail-label\">特点：</span>\n                            <span class=\"detail-content\">适合数组、结构体等需要初始化的数据结构</span>\n                        </div>\n                        <div class=\"code-block\">\n                            <pre><code class=\"language-c\">// calloc 使用示例\nint *scores = (int*)calloc(5, sizeof(int));\n                        </div>\n                        <div class=\"memory-visualization\">\n                            <div class=\"memory-block zero\">0</div>\n                            <div class=\"memory-block zero\">0</div>\n                            <div class=\"memory-block zero\">0</div>\n                            <div class=\"memory-block zero\">0</div>\n                            <div class=\"memory-block zero\">0</div>\n                            <div style=\"margin-left: 20px; color: #7f8c8d; font-size: 14px;\">\n                                <i class=\"fas fa-arrow-right\"></i> calloc分配的内存全部初始化为0\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <!-- Realloc 函数卡片 -->\n                <div class=\"function-card\">\n                    <div class=\"card-header\">\n                        <div class=\"function-icon realloc-icon\">\n                            <i class=\"fas fa-expand-alt\"></i>\n                        </div>\n                        <div>\n                            <h3 class=\"function-title\">realloc 函数</h3>\n                            <p class=\"function-subtitle\">调整已分配内存的大小</p>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"function-details\">\n                        <div','{}',NULL,0,1773720000,1773720000),(58,'d2191990-b108-4b42-8218-35c46b7c4b86',6,'slide_6','常见内存错误与调试','content','<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"zh-CN\">\n<head>\n<meta charset=\"UTF-8\" />\n<meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\" />\n<title>常见内存错误与调试 - C语言第四次课</title>\n<link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css\">\n<script src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/chart.js\"></script>\n<style>\n    * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }\n    html, body {\n        width: 100%;\n        height: 100%;\n        overflow: hidden;\n        background: #edf1eb;\n        font-family: \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"PingFang SC\", \"Noto Sans SC\", sans-serif;\n        color: #335239;\n    }\n    .slide-container {\n        width: 100vw;\n        height: 100vh;\n        display: flex;\n        align-items: center;\n        justify-content: center;\n    }\n    .slide {\n        width: 1280px;\n        height: 720px;\n        position: relative;\n        overflow: hidden;\n        transform-origin: center center;\n        border-radius: 16px;\n        background: linear-gradient(180deg, #f8faf6 0%, #f2f5ef 100%);\n        box-shadow: 0 18px 42px rgba(0,0,0,.14);\n    }\n\n    /* 页眉 - 严格保持原样 */\n    .header {\n        position: absolute;\n        left: 30px;\n        right: 30px;\n        top: 24px;\n        display: grid;\n        grid-template-columns: 1fr auto;\n        gap: 20px;\n        align-items: start;\n        z-index: 30;\n    }\n    .header h1 {\n        font-size: 28px;\n        line-height: 1.2;\n        color: #48724a;\n        font-weight: 900;\n        letter-spacing: .4px;\n    }\n    .header p {\n        margin-top: 7px;\n        font-size: 12px;\n        color: #7e8e7f;\n        line-height: 1.55;\n        max-width: 650px;\n    }\n\n    .main-tabs {\n        display: flex;\n        gap: 10px;\n        align-items: center;\n        flex-wrap: wrap;\n        justify-content: flex-end;\n    }\n    .main-tab {\n        border: 1px solid rgba(90,121,80,.18);\n        background: rgba(255,255,255,.92);\n        color: #5f7860;\n        border-radius: 999px;\n        padding: 9px 16px;\n        font-size: 14px;\n        font-weight: 800;\n        cursor: pointer;\n        transition: all .18s ease;\n    }\n    .main-tab.active {\n        background: #4e7b47;\n        color: #fff;\n        box-shadow: 0 8px 18px rgba(78,123,71,.28);\n    }\n\n    /* 主要内容区域 - 创意设计部分 */\n    .content-area {\n        position: absolute;\n        left: 28px;\n        right: 28px;\n        top: 98px;\n        bottom: 26px;\n        display: flex;\n        flex-direction: column;\n        padding: 20px 0;\n    }\n\n    .page-title {\n        text-align: center;\n        margin-bottom: 30px;\n        position: relative;\n    }\n    .page-title h2 {\n        font-size: 36px;\n        color: #4a7b43;\n        font-weight: 900;\n        margin-bottom: 8px;\n        letter-spacing: 1px;\n    }\n    .page-title .subtitle {\n        font-size: 16px;\n        color: #7e8e7f;\n        font-weight: 500;\n    }\n    .title-decoration {\n        position: absolute;\n        bottom: -10px;\n        left: 50%;\n        transform: translateX(-50%);\n        width: 120px;\n        height: 4px;\n        background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, #7da965, transparent);\n        border-radius: 2px;\n    }\n\n    /* 内存错误网格布局 */\n    .errors-grid {\n        flex: 1;\n        display: grid;\n        grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);\n        grid-template-rows: repeat(2, 1fr);\n        gap: 24px;\n        padding: 0 20px;\n        margin-bottom: 20px;\n    }\n\n    .error-card {\n        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95);\n        border-radius: 20px;\n        padding: 24px;\n        display: flex;\n        flex-direction: column;\n        align-items: center;\n        justify-content: center;\n        text-align: center;\n        box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);\n        border: 1px solid rgba(135, 169, 127, 0.15);\n        transition: all 0.3s ease;\n        position: relative;\n        overflow: hidden;\n    }\n    .error-card:hover {\n        transform: translateY(-5px);\n        box-shadow: 0 15px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);\n    }\n\n    .error-icon {\n        width: 80px;\n        height: 80px;\n        border-radius: 50%;\n        display: flex;\n        align-items: center;\n        justify-content: center;\n        margin-bottom: 18px;\n        font-size: 32px;\n        color: white;\n        position: relative;\n    }\n\n    .error-name {\n        font-size: 20px;\n        font-weight: 900;\n        color: #335239;\n        margin-bottom: 6px;\n    }\n    .error-en {\n        font-size: 14px;\n        color: #7e8e7f;\n        font-weight: 600;\n        margin-bottom: 12px;\n        letter-spacing: 0.5px;\n    }\n    .error-desc {\n        font-size: 13px;\n        color: #607163;\n        line-height: 1.5;\n        max-width: 90%;\n    }\n\n    /* 特定错误卡片样式 */\n    .leak .error-icon {\n        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #E67E22, #F39C12);\n        box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(230, 126, 34, 0.3);\n    }\n    .dangling .error-icon {\n        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #C0392B, #E74C3C);\n        box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(192, 57, 43, 0.3);\n    }\n    .double .error-icon {\n        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #8E44AD, #9B59B6);\n        box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(142, 68, 173, 0.3);\n    }\n    .bounds .error-icon {\n        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #D35400, #E67E22);\n        box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(211, 84, 0, 0.3);\n    }\n\n    /* 工具卡片特殊样式 */\n    .tool-card {\n        grid-column: span 1;\n        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #27AE60, #2ECC71);\n        color: white;\n        border: none;\n    }\n    .tool-card .error-icon {\n        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);\n        border: 3px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);\n    }\n    .tool-card .error-name,\n    .tool-card .error-en,\n    .tool-card .error-desc {\n        color: white;\n    }\n    .tool-card .error-desc {\n        opacity: 0.9;\n    }\n\n    /* 工具区域 */\n    .tool-section {\n        background: linear-gradient(90deg, #f7faf4, #f2f7ef);\n        border-radius: 20px;\n        padding: 25px 30px;\n        margin: 0 20px;\n        border: 1px solid #e3ece0;\n        display: flex;\n        align-items: center;\n        justify-content: space-between;\n        box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);\n    }\n    .tool-info {\n        flex: 1;\n    }\n    .tool-title {\n        font-size: 22px;\n        color: #4a7b43;\n        font-weight: 900;\n        margin-bottom: 8px;\n        display: flex;\n        align-items: center;\n        gap: 10px;\n    }\n    .tool-title i {\n        color: #27AE60;\n    }\n    .tool-desc {\n        font-size: 15px;\n        color: #607163;\n        line-height: 1.6;\n        max-width: 80%;\n    }\n    .tool-visual {\n        width: 180px;\n        height: 120px;\n        background: white;\n        border-radius: 12px;\n        display: flex;\n        align-items: center;\n        justify-content: center;\n        border: 1px solid #e3ece0;\n        position: relative;\n        overflow: hidden;\n    }\n    .tool-visual::before {\n        content: \"\";\n        position: absolute;\n        top: 0;\n        left: 0;\n        right: 0;\n        height: 4px;\n        background: linear-gradient(90deg, #27AE60, #2ECC71);\n    }\n    .code-snippet {\n        font-family: \'Courier New\', monospace;\n        font-size: 13px;\n        color: #335239;\n        text-align: left;\n        padding: 10px;\n    }\n    .code-snippet .line {\n        margin-bottom: 4px;\n    }\n    .code-snippet .comment {\n        color: #7e8e7f;\n    }\n    .code-snippet .command {\n        color: #27AE60;\n        font-weight: bold;\n    }\n\n    /* 装饰元素 */\n    .decoration {\n        position: absolute;\n        z-index: -1;\n    }\n    .decoration.circle-1 {\n        width: 120px;\n        height: 120px;\n        border-radius: 50%;\n        background: rgba(125, 169, 101, 0.08);\n        top: 120px;\n        left: 50px;\n    }\n    .decoration.circle-2 {\n        width: 80px;\n        height: 80px;\n        border-radius: 50%;\n        background: rgba(78, 123, 71, 0.05);\n        bottom: 100px;\n        right: 60px;\n    }\n    .decoration.line-1 {\n        width: 100%;\n        height: 1px;\n        background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, rgba(125, 169, 101, 0.2), transparent);\n        top: 180px;\n        left: 0;\n    }\n\n    /* 页脚 - 严格保持原样 */\n    .footer {\n        position: absolute;\n        bottom: 16px;\n        left: 0;\n        right: 0;\n        text-align: center;\n        font-size: 14px;\n        color: #7e8e7f;\n        z-index: 30;\n    }\n    .page-number {\n        display: inline-block;\n        padding: 6px 16px;\n        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);\n        border-radius: 999px;\n        border: 1px solid rgba(90, 121, 80, 0.15);\n        font-weight: 700;\n    }\n\n    /* 响应式调整 */\n    @media (max-width: 1350px) {\n        .errors-grid {\n            gap: 20px;\n            padding: 0 15px;\n        }\n        .error-card {\n            padding: 20px;\n        }\n    }\n</style>\n</head>\n<body>\n<div class=\"slide-container\">\n    <div class=\"slide\">\n        <!-- 页眉 - 严格保持原样 -->\n        <div class=\"header\">\n            <div>\n                <h1>C语言第四次课：内存管理</h1>\n                <p>深入理解内存错误类型与调试方法，掌握常见问题的识别与解决技巧</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"main-tabs\">\n                <div class=\"main-tab active\">内容页</div>\n                <div class=\"main-tab\">知识点</div>\n                <div class=\"main-tab\">案例</div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n\n        <!-- 主要内容区域 - 创意设计部分 -->\n        <div class=\"content-area\">\n            <!-- 页面标题 -->\n            <div class=\"page-title\">\n                <h2>常见内存错误与调试</h2>\n                <div class=\"subtitle\">识别、诊断与解决内存相关问题的系统方法</div>\n                <div class=\"title-decoration\"></div>\n            </div>\n\n            <!-- 内存错误网格 -->\n            <div class=\"errors-grid\">\n                <!-- 内存泄漏 -->\n                <div class=\"error-card leak\">\n                    <div class=\"error-icon\">\n                        <i class=\"fas fa-tint\"></i>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"error-name\">内存泄漏</div>\n                    <div class=\"error-en\">Memory Leak</div>\n                    <div class=\"error-desc\">已分配的内存未能释放，导致资源逐渐耗尽</div>\n                </div>\n\n                <!-- 野指针 -->\n                <div class=\"error-card dangling\">\n                    <div class=\"error-icon\">\n                        <i class=\"fas fa-bullseye\"></i>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"error-name\">野指针</div>\n                    <div class=\"error-en\">Dangling Pointer</div>\n                    <div class=\"error-desc\">指向已释放或无效内存区域的指针</div>\n                </div>\n\n                <!-- 重复释放 -->\n                <div class=\"error-card double\">\n                    <div class=\"error-icon\">\n                        <i class=\"fas fa-trash-restore\"></i>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"error-name\">重复释放</div>\n                    <div class=\"error-en\">Double Free</div>\n                    <div class=\"error-desc\">对同一内存区域进行多次释放操作</div>\n                </div>\n\n                <!-- 越界访问 -->\n                <div class=\"error-card bounds\">\n                    <div class=\"error-icon\">\n                        <i class=\"fas fa-expand-alt\"></i>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"error-name\">越界访问</div>\n                    <div class=\"error-en\">Out of Bounds</div>\n                    <div class=\"error-desc\">访问数组或缓冲区之外的内存区域</div>\n                </div>\n\n                <!-- 检测工具 -->\n                <div class=\"error-card tool-card\">\n                    <div class=\"error-icon\">\n                        <i class=\"fas fa-search\"></i>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"error-name\">检测工具</div>\n                    <div class=\"error-en\">Detection Tools</div>\n                    <div class=\"error-desc\">使用专业工具定位内存问题</div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n\n            <!-- 工具区域 -->\n            <div class=\"tool-section\">\n                <div class=\"tool-info\">\n                    <div class=\"tool-title\">\n                        <i class=\"fas fa-tools\"></i>\n                        使用Valgrind等工具进行系统检测\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"tool-desc\">\n                        Valgrind是一款强大的内存调试工具，可以检测内存泄漏、非法内存访问、使用未初始化值等问题。\n                        配合Memcheck工具，能够提供详细的问题报告和定位信息。\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"tool-visual\">\n                    <div class=\"code-snippet\">\n                        <div class=\"line\"><span class=\"command\">$ valgrind</span> --tool=memcheck ./program</div>\n                        <div class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># 检测内存泄漏</span></div>\n                        <div class=\"line\"><span class=\"command\">$ valgrind</span> --leak-check=full ./program</div>\n                        <div class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># 详细报告</span></div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n\n        <!-- 装饰元素 -->\n        <div class=\"decoration circle-1\"></div>\n        <div class=\"decoration circle-2\"></div>\n        <div class=\"decoration line-1\"></div>\n\n        <!-- 页脚 - 严格保持原样 -->\n        <div class=\"footer\">\n            <span class=\"page-number\">7 / 10</span>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</div>\n\n<script>\n    // 添加卡片交互效果\n    document.addEventListener(\'DOMContentLoaded\', function() {\n        const cards = document.querySelectorAll(\'.error-card\');\n        \n        cards.forEach(card => {\n            card.addEventListener(\'mouseenter\', function() {\n                const icon = this.querySelector(\'.error-icon\');\n                icon.style.transform = \'scale(1.1)\';\n            });\n            \n            card.addEventListener(\'mouseleave\', function() {\n                const icon = this.querySelector(\'.error-icon\');\n                icon.style.transform = \'scale(1)\';\n            });\n        });\n        \n        // 模拟工具区域的动态效果\n        const toolVisual = document.querySelector(\'.tool-visual\');\n        setInterval(() => {\n            toolVisual.style.boxShadow = \'0 0 0 2px rgba(39, 174, 96, 0.3)\';\n            setTimeout(() => {\n                toolVisual.style.boxShadow = \'0 0 0 0 rgba(39, 174, 96, 0)\';\n            }, 500);\n        }, 3000);\n    });\n</script>\n</body>\n</html>','{}',NULL,0,1773720000,1773720000),(59,'d2191990-b108-4b42-8218-35c46b7c4b86',7,'slide_7','综合案例：动态数组的实现','content','<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"zh-CN\">\n<head>\n<meta charset=\"UTF-8\" />\n<meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\" />\n<title>第8页：综合案例：动态数组的实现</title>\n<link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css\">\n<link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/prism/1.29.0/themes/prism-tomorrow.min.css\">\n<script src=\"https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/prism/1.29.0/prism.min.js\"></script>\n<script src=\"https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/prism/1.29.0/components/prism-c.min.js\"></script>\n<style>\n    * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }\n    html, body {\n        width: 100%;\n        height: 100%;\n        overflow: hidden;\n        background: #edf1eb;\n        font-family: \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"PingFang SC\", \"Noto Sans SC\", sans-serif;\n        color: #335239;\n    }\n    .slide-container {\n        width: 100vw;\n        height: 100vh;\n        display: flex;\n        align-items: center;\n        justify-content: center;\n    }\n    .slide {\n        width: 1280px;\n        height: 720px;\n        position: relative;\n        overflow: hidden;\n        transform-origin: center center;\n        border-radius: 16px;\n        background: linear-gradient(180deg, #f8faf6 0%, #f2f5ef 100%);\n        box-shadow: 0 18px 42px rgba(0,0,0,.14);\n    }\n    /* 页眉 - 严格保持原样 */\n    .header {\n        position: absolute;\n        left: 30px;\n        right: 30px;\n        top: 24px;\n        display: grid;\n        grid-template-columns: 1fr auto;\n        gap: 20px;\n        align-items: start;\n        z-index: 30;\n    }\n    .header h1 {\n        font-size: 28px;\n        line-height: 1.2;\n        color: #48724a;\n        font-weight: 900;\n        letter-spacing: .4px;\n    }\n    .header p {\n        margin-top: 7px;\n        font-size: 12px;\n        color: #7e8e7f;\n        line-height: 1.55;\n        max-width: 650px;\n    }\n    .main-tabs {\n        display: flex;\n        gap: 10px;\n        align-items: center;\n        flex-wrap: wrap;\n        justify-content: flex-end;\n    }\n    .main-tab {\n        border: 1px solid rgba(90,121,80,.18);\n        background: rgba(255,255,255,.92);\n        color: #5f7860;\n        border-radius: 999px;\n        padding: 9px 16px;\n        font-size: 14px;\n        font-weight: 800;\n        cursor: pointer;\n        transition: all .18s ease;\n    }\n    .main-tab.active {\n        background: #4e7b47;\n        color: #fff;\n        box-shadow: 0 8px 18px rgba(78,123,71,.28);\n    }\n    /* 主要内容区域 - 可创意设计 */\n    .content-area {\n        position: absolute;\n        left: 30px;\n        right: 30px;\n        top: 98px;\n        bottom: 60px;\n        display: flex;\n        flex-direction: column;\n        gap: 16px;\n    }\n    /* 页脚 - 严格保持原样 */\n    .footer {\n        position: absolute;\n        left: 30px;\n        right: 30px;\n        bottom: 20px;\n        display: flex;\n        justify-content: space-between;\n        align-items: center;\n        font-size: 12px;\n        color: #7e8e7f;\n        z-index: 30;\n    }\n    .footer .page-number {\n        font-weight: 700;\n        color: #5a7a55;\n    }\n    .footer .decorative-line {\n        flex-grow: 1;\n        height: 1px;\n        background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, rgba(90,121,80,.2), transparent);\n        margin: 0 15px;\n    }\n    /* 创意设计部分 */\n    .page-title {\n        font-size: 32px;\n        font-weight: 900;\n        color: #4a7b43;\n        margin-bottom: 8px;\n        display: flex;\n        align-items: center;\n        gap: 12px;\n    }\n    .page-title i {\n        color: #6fa642;\n        font-size: 28px;\n    }\n    .subtitle {\n        font-size: 16px;\n        color: #788874;\n        margin-bottom: 20px;\n        font-weight: 500;\n    }\n    .main-content {\n        display: flex;\n        flex-grow: 1;\n        gap: 24px;\n        height: calc(100% - 80px);\n    }\n    .left-panel {\n        flex: 0 0 380px;\n        display: flex;\n        flex-direction: column;\n        gap: 18px;\n    }\n    .feature-card {\n        background: rgba(255,255,255,.92);\n        border-radius: 20px;\n        padding: 20px;\n        border: 1px solid rgba(87,124,79,.12);\n        box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(0,0,0,.05);\n        transition: transform 0.3s ease;\n        flex-grow: 1;\n        display: flex;\n        flex-direction: column;\n    }\n    .feature-card:hover {\n        transform: translateY(-5px);\n        box-shadow: 0 12px 24px rgba(0,0,0,.08);\n    }\n    .feature-header {\n        display: flex;\n        align-items: center;\n        gap: 12px;\n        margin-bottom: 15px;\n        padding-bottom: 12px;\n        border-bottom: 1px dashed #e3ece0;\n    }\n    .feature-icon {\n        width: 40px;\n        height: 40px;\n        border-radius: 12px;\n        display: flex;\n        align-items: center;\n        justify-content: center;\n        font-size: 18px;\n        color: white;\n    }\n    .icon-1 { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #6CABE7, #4A8FD8); }\n    .icon-2 { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #00CC88, #00AA6E); }\n    .icon-3 { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #FF9966, #FF7744); }\n    .icon-4 { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #9D7BFF, #7B5AEA); }\n    .feature-title {\n        font-size: 18px;\n        font-weight: 800;\n        color: #4a7b43;\n    }\n    .feature-desc {\n        font-size: 14px;\n        color: #607163;\n        line-height: 1.6;\n        flex-grow: 1;\n    }\n    .right-panel {\n        flex: 1;\n        display: flex;\n        flex-direction: column;\n        gap: 18px;\n    }\n    .code-section {\n        background: #1e1e1e;\n        border-radius: 20px;\n        overflow: hidden;\n        flex-grow: 1;\n        display: flex;\n        flex-direction: column;\n        box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,.2);\n    }\n    .code-header {\n        background: #2d2d2d;\n        padding: 15px 20px;\n        display: flex;\n        justify-content: space-between;\n        align-items: center;\n        border-bottom: 1px solid #3d3d3d;\n    }\n    .code-title {\n        color: #f0f0f0;\n        font-size: 16px;\n        font-weight: 700;\n        display: flex;\n        align-items: center;\n        gap: 10px;\n    }\n    .code-actions {\n        display: flex;\n        gap: 10px;\n    }\n    .code-btn {\n        background: #3d3d3d;\n        border: none;\n        color: #aaa;\n        padding: 6px 12px;\n        border-radius: 6px;\n        font-size: 12px;\n        cursor: pointer;\n        transition: all 0.2s;\n    }\n    .code-btn:hover {\n        background: #4a4a4a;\n        color: #fff;\n    }\n    .code-content {\n        flex-grow: 1;\n        padding: 20px;\n        overflow: auto;\n        font-family: \'Consolas\', \'Monaco\', monospace;\n        font-size: 14px;\n        line-height: 1.5;\n    }\n    .code-content pre {\n        margin: 0;\n        color: #d4d4d4;\n    }\n    .code-line {\n        display: flex;\n        margin-bottom: 4px;\n    }\n    .line-number {\n        color: #6a9955;\n        min-width: 40px;\n        text-align: right;\n        padding-right: 15px;\n        user-select: none;\n    }\n    .line-code {\n        flex-grow: 1;\n    }\n    .keyword { color: #569cd6; }\n    .type { color: #4ec9b0; }\n    .function { color: #dcdcaa; }\n    .string { color: #ce9178; }\n    .comment { color: #6a9955; }\n    .number { color: #b5cea8; }\n    .macro { color: #c586c0; }\n    .thought-section {\n        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f7faf4, #f2f7ef);\n        border-radius: 20px;\n        padding: 20px;\n        border: 1px solid #e3ece0;\n        display: flex;\n        align-items: center;\n        gap: 20px;\n    }\n    .thought-icon {\n        width: 60px;\n        height: 60px;\n        border-radius: 50%;\n        background: #4e7b47;\n        display: flex;\n        align-items: center;\n        justify-content: center;\n        color: white;\n        font-size: 24px;\n        flex-shrink: 0;\n    }\n    .thought-content {\n        flex-grow: 1;\n    }\n    .thought-title {\n        font-size: 18px;\n        font-weight: 800;\n        color: #4a7b43;\n        margin-bottom: 8px;\n    }\n    .thought-desc {\n        font-size: 14px;\n        color: #607163;\n        line-height: 1.6;\n    }\n    /* 动态数组可视化 */\n    .array-visualization {\n        position: absolute;\n        right: 40px;\n        top: 120px;\n        width: 300px;\n        height: 180px;\n        background: rgba(255,255,255,.8);\n        border-radius: 16px;\n        padding: 15px;\n        border: 1px solid rgba(87,124,79,.15);\n        box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(0,0,0,.08);\n        z-index: 10;\n        display: none; /* 默认隐藏，可通过交互显示 */\n    }\n    .visual-title {\n        font-size: 14px;\n        font-weight: 700;\n        color: #4a7b43;\n        margin-bottom: 10px;\n        text-align: center;\n    }\n    .array-container {\n        display: flex;\n        align-items: center;\n        justify-content: center;\n        gap: 8px;\n        margin-top: 10px;\n    }\n    .array-element {\n        width: 40px;\n        height: 40px;\n        border-radius: 8px;\n        display: flex;\n        align-items: center;\n        justify-content: center;\n        font-weight: 700;\n        color: white;\n        background: #6fa642;\n        transition: all 0.3s ease;\n    }\n    .array-element.empty {\n        background: #e3ece0;\n        color: #a0b09c;\n    }\n    .capacity-bar {\n        height: 6px;\n        background: #e3ece0;\n        border-radius: 3px;\n        margin-top: 15px;\n        overflow: hidden;\n    }\n    .used-capacity {\n        height: 100%;\n        background: #6fa642;\n        border-radius: 3px;\n        width: 60%;\n        transition: width 0.5s ease;\n    }\n    /* 装饰元素 */\n    .decoration-circle {\n        position: absolute;\n        border-radius: 50%;\n        opacity: 0.1;\n        z-index: 1;\n    }\n    .circle-1 {\n        width: 120px;\n        height: 120px;\n        background: #6fa642;\n        right: 80px;\n        top: 180px;\n    }\n    .circle-2 {\n        width: 80px;\n        height: 80px;\n        background: #4e7b47;\n        left: 100px;\n        bottom: 120px;\n    }\n    .circle-3 {\n        width: 60px;\n        height: 60px;\n        background: #c9d97c;\n        right: 200px;\n        bottom: 80px;\n    }\n</style>\n</head>\n<body>\n<div class=\"slide-container\">\n    <div class=\"slide\">\n        <!-- 页眉 - 严格保持原样 -->\n        <div class=\"header\">\n            <div>\n                <h1>食品药品职业学院 PPT 模板描述文件（字段规范版）</h1>\n                <p>参照 template.html 的\"单文件、自包含、固定 1280×720、响应式缩放、占位符与规则说明\"写法，在 v3 的子版式拆分基础上，继续把字段命名、选型规则、禁用场景和母版约束标准化，方便后续直接拿来生成新的 PPT。</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"main-tabs\">\n                <div class=\"main-tab active\">内容系统</div>\n                <div class=\"main-tab\">数据系统</div>\n                <div class=\"main-tab\">目录系统</div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n        <!-- 主要内容区域 - 创意设计 -->\n        <div class=\"content-area\">\n            <div class=\"page-title\">\n                <i class=\"fas fa-code\"></i>\n                综合案例：动态数组的实现\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"subtitle\">一种可自适应容量的高效数据存储方案 | 从设计到封装的完整实践路径</div>\n            <div class=\"main-content\">\n                <!-- 左侧功能模块 -->\n                <div class=\"left-panel\">\n                    <div class=\"feature-card\">\n                        <div class=\"feature-header\">\n                            <div class=\"feature-icon icon-1\">\n                                <i class=\"fas fa-drafting-compass\"></i>\n                            </div>\n                            <div class=\"feature-title\">设计可动态扩容的整型数组结构</div>\n                        </div>\n                        <div class=\"feature-desc\">\n                            定义动态数组的核心数据结构，包含数据指针、当前大小和总容量。设计扩容策略（通常为2倍增长），平衡空间效率与时间性能。\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"feature-card\">\n                        <div class=\"feature-header\">\n                            <div class=\"feature-icon icon-2\">\n                                <i class=\"fas fa-plus-circle\"></i>\n                            </div>\n                            <div class=\"feature-title\">实现初始化、添加、删除、扩容等功能</div>\n                        </div>\n                        <div class=\"feature-desc\">\n                            编写核心操作函数：初始化分配内存、尾部添加元素（自动扩容）、删除指定位置元素（移动后续元素）、容量不足时自动扩容并迁移数据。\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"feature-card\">\n                        <div class=\"feature-header\">\n                            <div class=\"feature-icon icon-3\">\n                                <i class=\"fas fa-laptop-code\"></i>\n                            </div>\n                            <div class=\"feature-title\">代码演示与逐行讲解</div>\n                        </div>\n                        <div class=\"feature-desc\">\n                            通过实际代码展示动态数组的实现细节，逐行解析关键算法、边界处理、内存管理和性能考量，建立从理论到实践的直观映射。\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"feature-card\">\n                        <div class=\"feature-header\">\n                            <div class=\"feature-icon icon-4\">\n                                <i class=\"fas fa-cube\"></i>\n                            </div>\n                            <div class=\"feature-title\">思考：如何封装成通用的动态数组？</div>\n                        </div>\n                        <div class=\"feature-desc\">\n                            从具体类型抽象到通用模板，探讨类型安全、内存管理、迭代器设计等高级话题，为后续学习STL等标准库奠定基础。\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <!-- 右侧代码演示区 -->\n                <div class=\"right-panel\">\n                    <div class=\"code-section\">\n                        <div class=\"code-header\">\n                            <div class=\"code-title\">\n                                <i class=\"fas fa-file-code\"></i>\n                                dynamic_array.c - 动态数组核心实现\n                            </div>\n                            <div class=\"code-actions\">\n                                <button class=\"code-btn\"><i class=\"fas fa-play\"></i> 运行</button>\n                                <button class=\"code-btn\"><i class=\"fas fa-expand\"></i> 展开</button>\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                        <div class=\"code-content\">\n                            <pre><code class=\"language-c\">// 动态数组结构定义\ntypedef struct {\n    int *data;      // 数据指针\n    size_t size;    // 当前元素数量\n    size_t capacity;// 总容量\n} DynamicArray;\nDynamicArray* da_init(size_t init_capacity) {\n    DynamicArray *arr = malloc(sizeof(DynamicArray));\n    arr->data = malloc(init_capacity * sizeof(int));\n    arr->size = 0;\n    arr','{}',NULL,0,1773720000,1773720000),(60,'d2191990-b108-4b42-8218-35c46b7c4b86',8,'slide_8','练习与思考题','content','<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"zh-CN\">\n<head>\n<meta charset=\"UTF-8\" />\n<meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\" />\n<title>练习与思考题 - C语言第四次课</title>\n<link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css\">\n<link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/prism/1.29.0/themes/prism-tomorrow.min.css\">\n<script src=\"https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/prism/1.29.0/prism.min.js\"></script>\n<script src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/chart.js\"></script>\n<style>\n    * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }\n    html, body {\n        width: 100%;\n        height: 100%;\n        overflow: hidden;\n        background: #edf1eb;\n        font-family: \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"PingFang SC\", \"Noto Sans SC\", sans-serif;\n        color: #335239;\n    }\n    .slide-container {\n        width: 100vw;\n        height: 100vh;\n        display: flex;\n        align-items: center;\n        justify-content: center;\n    }\n    .slide {\n        width: 1280px;\n        height: 720px;\n        position: relative;\n        overflow: hidden;\n        transform-origin: center center;\n        border-radius: 16px;\n        background: linear-gradient(180deg, #f8faf6 0%, #f2f5ef 100%);\n        box-shadow: 0 18px 42px rgba(0,0,0,.14);\n    }\n    /* 页眉 - 严格保持原样 */\n    .header {\n        position: absolute;\n        left: 30px;\n        right: 30px;\n        top: 24px;\n        display: grid;\n        grid-template-columns: 1fr auto;\n        gap: 20px;\n        align-items: start;\n        z-index: 30;\n    }\n    .header h1 {\n        font-size: 28px;\n        line-height: 1.2;\n        color: #48724a;\n        font-weight: 900;\n        letter-spacing: .4px;\n    }\n    .header p {\n        margin-top: 7px;\n        font-size: 12px;\n        color: #7e8e7f;\n        line-height: 1.55;\n        max-width: 650px;\n    }\n    .main-tabs {\n        display: flex;\n        gap: 10px;\n        align-items: center;\n        flex-wrap: wrap;\n        justify-content: flex-end;\n    }\n    .main-tab {\n        border: 1px solid rgba(90,121,80,.18);\n        background: rgba(255,255,255,.92);\n        color: #5f7860;\n        border-radius: 999px;\n        padding: 9px 16px;\n        font-size: 14px;\n        font-weight: 800;\n        cursor: pointer;\n        transition: all .18s ease;\n    }\n    .main-tab.active {\n        background: #4e7b47;\n        color: #fff;\n        box-shadow: 0 8px 18px rgba(78,123,71,.28);\n    }\n    /* 主要内容区域 - 可创意设计 */\n    .main-content {\n        position: absolute;\n        left: 30px;\n        right: 30px;\n        top: 98px;\n        bottom: 60px;\n        display: flex;\n        flex-direction: column;\n        gap: 20px;\n    }\n    /* 页脚 - 严格保持原样 */\n    .footer {\n        position: absolute;\n        left: 30px;\n        right: 30px;\n        bottom: 20px;\n        display: flex;\n        justify-content: space-between;\n        align-items: center;\n        z-index: 30;\n    }\n    .footer .page-number {\n        font-size: 14px;\n        color: #7e8e7f;\n        font-weight: 600;\n    }\n    .footer .decorative-line {\n        flex-grow: 1;\n        height: 1px;\n        background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, rgba(90,121,80,.2), transparent);\n        margin: 0 20px;\n    }\n    .footer .school-name {\n        font-size: 12px;\n        color: #7e8e7f;\n    }\n    /* 创意设计区域 */\n    .page-title {\n        text-align: center;\n        margin-bottom: 10px;\n    }\n    .page-title h2 {\n        font-size: 36px;\n        color: #4e7b47;\n        font-weight: 900;\n        letter-spacing: 1px;\n        margin-bottom: 8px;\n        position: relative;\n        display: inline-block;\n    }\n    .page-title h2::after {\n        content: \'\';\n        position: absolute;\n        bottom: -8px;\n        left: 50%;\n        transform: translateX(-50%);\n        width: 120px;\n        height: 4px;\n        background: linear-gradient(90deg, #4e7b47, #8cb267);\n        border-radius: 2px;\n    }\n    .page-title p {\n        font-size: 16px;\n        color: #7e8e7f;\n        font-weight: 500;\n    }\n    .content-grid {\n        display: grid;\n        grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);\n        gap: 20px;\n        height: 100%;\n        flex-grow: 1;\n    }\n    .content-card {\n        background: rgba(255,255,255,.95);\n        border-radius: 20px;\n        padding: 24px;\n        display: flex;\n        flex-direction: column;\n        border: 1px solid rgba(87,124,79,.12);\n        box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(0,0,0,.06);\n        transition: all 0.3s ease;\n        position: relative;\n        overflow: hidden;\n    }\n    .content-card:hover {\n        transform: translateY(-5px);\n        box-shadow: 0 12px 32px rgba(78,123,71,.15);\n    }\n    .card-header {\n        display: flex;\n        align-items: center;\n        margin-bottom: 20px;\n        padding-bottom: 15px;\n        border-bottom: 2px solid rgba(78,123,71,.1);\n    }\n    .card-icon {\n        width: 60px;\n        height: 60px;\n        border-radius: 50%;\n        display: flex;\n        align-items: center;\n        justify-content: center;\n        margin-right: 18px;\n        font-size: 28px;\n        color: white;\n        flex-shrink: 0;\n    }\n    .card-title {\n        flex-grow: 1;\n    }\n    .card-title h3 {\n        font-size: 22px;\n        color: #335239;\n        font-weight: 800;\n        margin-bottom: 5px;\n    }\n    .card-title .subtitle {\n        font-size: 14px;\n        color: #7e8e7f;\n        font-weight: 500;\n    }\n    .card-difficulty {\n        display: flex;\n        margin-top: 5px;\n    }\n    .star {\n        color: #FFC107;\n        font-size: 16px;\n        margin-right: 2px;\n    }\n    .card-content {\n        flex-grow: 1;\n        display: flex;\n        flex-direction: column;\n    }\n    .task-list {\n        list-style: none;\n        margin-bottom: 20px;\n        flex-grow: 1;\n    }\n    .task-list li {\n        position: relative;\n        padding-left: 22px;\n        margin-bottom: 12px;\n        font-size: 15px;\n        color: #607163;\n        line-height: 1.5;\n    }\n    .task-list li::before {\n        content: \"▶\";\n        position: absolute;\n        left: 0;\n        top: 2px;\n        color: #7da965;\n        font-size: 12px;\n    }\n    .code-preview {\n        background: #2d2d2d;\n        border-radius: 10px;\n        padding: 15px;\n        margin-top: 15px;\n        font-family: \'Consolas\', \'Monaco\', monospace;\n        font-size: 13px;\n        color: #f8f8f2;\n        line-height: 1.4;\n        overflow: hidden;\n        flex-grow: 1;\n    }\n    .code-preview .comment { color: #75715e; }\n    .code-preview .keyword { color: #66d9ef; }\n    .code-preview .function { color: #a6e22e; }\n    .code-preview .type { color: #f92672; }\n    .chart-container {\n        height: 180px;\n        margin-top: 15px;\n        position: relative;\n    }\n    .thinking-points {\n        background: #f8fbf6;\n        border-radius: 12px;\n        padding: 16px;\n        margin-top: 15px;\n        border-left: 4px solid #7da965;\n    }\n    .thinking-points p {\n        font-size: 14px;\n        color: #607163;\n        line-height: 1.6;\n        margin-bottom: 10px;\n    }\n    .thinking-points .question {\n        font-weight: 700;\n        color: #4e7b47;\n        margin-top: 12px;\n        display: block;\n    }\n    .next-lesson {\n        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f6faf4, #e8f1e5);\n        border-radius: 16px;\n        padding: 20px;\n        margin-top: 20px;\n        border: 2px dashed #bdd4b2;\n        display: flex;\n        align-items: center;\n        justify-content: space-between;\n    }\n    .next-lesson-content {\n        flex-grow: 1;\n    }\n    .next-lesson h4 {\n        font-size: 18px;\n        color: #4e7b47;\n        font-weight: 800;\n        margin-bottom: 8px;\n    }\n    .next-lesson p {\n        font-size: 14px;\n        color: #7e8e7f;\n    }\n    .next-lesson-icon {\n        font-size: 40px;\n        color: #7da965;\n        margin-left: 20px;\n    }\n    /* 卡片特定样式 */\n    .card-1 .card-icon { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #4A90E2, #5fa3ff); }\n    .card-2 .card-icon { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #F5A623, #ffb84d); }\n    .card-3 .card-icon { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #9013FE, #b150ff); }\n    /* 装饰元素 */\n    .decoration {\n        position: absolute;\n        z-index: 1;\n    }\n    .decoration-1 {\n        width: 80px;\n        height: 80px;\n        background: rgba(141, 190, 124, 0.1);\n        border-radius: 50%;\n        top: 120px;\n        left: 50px;\n    }\n    .decoration-2 {\n        width: 40px;\n        height: 40px;\n        background: rgba(125, 169, 101, 0.15);\n        border-radius: 50%;\n        bottom: 100px;\n        right: 80px;\n    }\n    .decoration-3 {\n        width: 120px;\n        height: 120px;\n        border: 2px dashed rgba(78, 123, 71, 0.2);\n        border-radius: 50%;\n        top: 180px;\n        right: 60px;\n    }\n    /* 响应式调整 */\n    @media (max-width: 1350px) {\n        .content-grid {\n            gap: 15px;\n        }\n        .content-card {\n            padding: 20px;\n        }\n    }\n</style>\n</head>\n<body>\n<div class=\"slide-container\">\n    <div class=\"slide\">\n        <!-- 页眉 - 严格保持原样 -->\n        <div class=\"header\">\n            <div>\n                <h1>食品药品职业学院 PPT 模板描述文件（字段规范版）</h1>\n                <p>参照 template.html 的\"单文件、自包含、固定 1280×720、响应式缩放、占位符与规则说明\"写法，在 v3 的子版式拆分基础上，继续把字段命名、选型规则、禁用场景和母版约束标准化，方便后续直接拿来生成新的 PPT。</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"main-tabs\">\n                <button class=\"main-tab\">封面系统</button>\n                <button class=\"main-tab\">目录系统</button>\n                <button class=\"main-tab active\">内容系统</button>\n                <button class=\"main-tab\">数据系统</button>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n        <!-- 主要内容区域 - 创意设计 -->\n        <div class=\"main-content\">\n            <div class=\"page-title\">\n                <h2>练习与思考题</h2>\n                <p>C语言第四次课 · 编程实验室实践区</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"content-grid\">\n                <!-- 练习1卡片 -->\n                <div class=\"content-card card-1\">\n                    <div class=\"card-header\">\n                        <div class=\"card-icon\">\n                            <i class=\"fas fa-calculator\"></i>\n                        </div>\n                        <div class=\"card-title\">\n                            <h3>练习1</h3>\n                            <div class=\"subtitle\">函数指针实战</div>\n                            <div class=\"card-difficulty\">\n                                <span class=\"star\">★</span>\n                                <span class=\"star\">★</span>\n                                <span class=\"star\" style=\"color:#ddd\">★</span>\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"card-content\">\n                        <ul class=\"task-list\">\n                            <li>使用函数指针实现四则运算计算器</li>\n                            <li>通过函数指针数组调用不同运算函数</li>\n                            <li>理解回调机制与接口设计</li>\n                            <li>支持加减乘除四种基本运算</li>\n                        </ul>\n                        <div class=\"code-preview\">\n                            <span class=\"comment\">// 函数指针数组示例</span><br>\n                            <span class=\"type\">int</span> (<span class=\"keyword\">*</span>ops[<span class=\"number\">4</span>])(<span class=\"type\">int</span>, <span class=\"type\">int</span>) = {<br>\n                            &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;add, <span class=\"comment\">// 加法</span><br>\n                            &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;sub, <span class=\"comment\">// 减法</span><br>\n                            &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;mul, <span class=\"comment\">// 乘法</span><br>\n                            &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;div&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"comment\">// 除法</span><br>\n                            };\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <!-- 练习2卡片 -->\n                <div class=\"content-card card-2\">\n                    <div class=\"card-header\">\n                        <div class=\"card-icon\">\n                            <i class=\"fas fa-chart-bar\"></i>\n                        </div>\n                        <div class=\"card-title\">\n                            <h3>练习2</h3>\n                            <div class=\"subtitle\">动态内存管理</div>\n                            <div class=\"card-difficulty\">\n                                <span class=\"star\">★</span>\n                                <span class=\"star\">★</span>\n                                <span class=\"star\">★</span>\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"card-content\">\n                        <ul class=\"task-list\">\n                            <li>使用动态内存管理学生成绩数组</li>\n                            <li>实现数组的动态扩容与缩容</li>\n                            <li>正确处理内存分配失败情况</li>\n                            <li>避免内存泄漏与野指针</li>\n                        </ul>\n                        <div class=\"chart-container\">\n                            <canvas id=\"memoryChart\"></canvas>\n                        </div>\n                        <div class=\"thinking-points\">\n                            <p><strong>关键点：</strong>malloc/free的正确使用，指针有效性检查，内存边界管理。</p>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <!-- 思考题卡片 -->\n                <div class=\"content-card card-3\">\n                    <div class=\"card-header\">\n                        <div class=\"card-icon\">\n                            <i class=\"fas fa-brain\"></i>\n                        </div>\n                        <div class=\"card-title\">\n                            <h3>思考</h3>\n                            <div class=\"subtitle\">大型项目中的重要性</div>\n                            <div class=\"card-difficulty\">\n                                <span class=\"star\">★</span>\n                                <span class=\"star\">★</span>\n                                <span class=\"star\" style=\"color:#ddd\">★</span>\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"card-content\">\n                        <div class=\"thinking-points\">\n                            <p>指针与内存管理在大型软件项目中的关键作用：</p>\n                            <p>• 模块间数据传递的效率优化</p>\n                            <p>• 资源管理的安全性与可靠性</p>\n                            <p>• 系统性能的关键影响因素</p>\n                            <p>• 代码可维护性的设计考量</p>\n                            <span class=\"question\">引导性问题：</span>\n                            <p>你遇到过哪些内存管理问题？如何设计可维护的指针接口？</p>\n                        </div>\n                        <div style=\"margin-top: 20px; padding: 12px; background: #f0f7ed; border-radius: 10px;\">\n                            <p style=\"font-size: 13px; color: #5a7a55; text-align: center;\">\n                                <i class=\"fas fa-lightbulb\" style=\"color: #FFC107; margin','{}',NULL,0,1773720000,1773720000),(61,'d2191990-b108-4b42-8218-35c46b7c4b86',9,'slide_9','总结与Q&A','content','<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"zh-CN\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>总结与Q&A - C语言第四次课</title>\n    <link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css\">\n    <script src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/chart.js\"></script>\n    <script src=\"https://polyfill.io/v3/polyfill.min.js?features=es6\"></script>\n    <script id=\"MathJax-script\" async src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/mathjax@3/es5/tex-mml-chtml.js\"></script>\n    <script src=\"https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/prism/1.29.0/prism.min.js\"></script>\n    <link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/prism/1.29.0/themes/prism-tomorrow.min.css\">\n    <style>\n        * {\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            box-sizing: border-box;\n        }\n        html, body {\n            width: 100%;\n            height: 100%;\n            overflow: hidden;\n            background: #edf1eb;\n            font-family: \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"PingFang SC\", \"Noto Sans SC\", sans-serif;\n            color: #335239;\n        }\n        .slide-container {\n            width: 100vw;\n            height: 100vh;\n            display: flex;\n            align-items: center;\n            justify-content: center;\n        }\n        .slide {\n            width: 1280px;\n            height: 720px;\n            position: relative;\n            overflow: hidden;\n            transform-origin: center center;\n            border-radius: 16px;\n            background: linear-gradient(180deg, #f8faf6 0%, #f2f5ef 100%);\n            box-shadow: 0 18px 42px rgba(0,0,0,.14);\n        }\n        /* 页眉 - 严格保持原样 */\n        .header {\n            position: absolute;\n            left: 30px;\n            right: 30px;\n            top: 24px;\n            display: grid;\n            grid-template-columns: 1fr auto;\n            gap: 20px;\n            align-items: start;\n            z-index: 30;\n        }\n        .header h1 {\n            font-size: 28px;\n            line-height: 1.2;\n            color: #48724a;\n            font-weight: 900;\n            letter-spacing: .4px;\n        }\n        .header p {\n            margin-top: 7px;\n            font-size: 12px;\n            color: #7e8e7f;\n            line-height: 1.55;\n            max-width: 650px;\n        }\n        .main-tabs {\n            display: flex;\n            gap: 10px;\n            align-items: center;\n            flex-wrap: wrap;\n            justify-content: flex-end;\n        }\n        .main-tab {\n            border: 1px solid rgba(90,121,80,.18);\n            background: rgba(255,255,255,.92);\n            color: #5f7860;\n            border-radius: 999px;\n            padding: 9px 16px;\n            font-size: 14px;\n            font-weight: 800;\n            cursor: pointer;\n            transition: all .18s ease;\n        }\n        .main-tab.active {\n            background: #4e7b47;\n            color: #fff;\n            box-shadow: 0 8px 18px rgba(78,123,71,.28);\n        }\n        /* 主要内容区域 */\n        .main-content {\n            position: absolute;\n            left: 28px;\n            right: 28px;\n            top: 98px;\n            bottom: 26px;\n            display: flex;\n            flex-direction: column;\n            gap: 20px;\n            padding: 20px 0;\n        }\n        /* 页面标题 */\n        .page-title {\n            text-align: center;\n            margin-bottom: 10px;\n        }\n        .page-title h2 {\n            font-size: 42px;\n            color: #4e874c;\n            font-weight: 900;\n            letter-spacing: 1px;\n            text-shadow: 0 2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);\n            position: relative;\n            display: inline-block;\n        }\n        .page-title h2::after {\n            content: \'\';\n            position: absolute;\n            bottom: -8px;\n            left: 10%;\n            width: 80%;\n            height: 4px;\n            background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, #7da965, transparent);\n            border-radius: 2px;\n        }\n        /* 内容容器 */\n        .content-container {\n            display: flex;\n            flex: 1;\n            gap: 20px;\n            height: calc(100% - 80px);\n        }\n        /* 左侧总结区域 */\n        .summary-section {\n            flex: 1;\n            display: flex;\n            flex-direction: column;\n            gap: 20px;\n        }\n        .summary-card {\n            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.95);\n            border-radius: 20px;\n            padding: 24px;\n            box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(78,123,71,0.12);\n            border: 1px solid rgba(87,124,79,.15);\n            height: 100%;\n            display: flex;\n            flex-direction: column;\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;\n        }\n        .summary-card:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-5px);\n            box-shadow: 0 12px 32px rgba(78,123,71,0.18);\n        }\n        .card-header {\n            display: flex;\n            align-items: center;\n            gap: 12px;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            padding-bottom: 12px;\n            border-bottom: 2px solid #e8f0e5;\n        }\n        .card-icon {\n            width: 48px;\n            height: 48px;\n            border-radius: 12px;\n            display: flex;\n            align-items: center;\n            justify-content: center;\n            font-size: 22px;\n            color: white;\n        }\n        .icon-knowledge {\n            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #4e874c, #7da965);\n        }\n        .icon-warning {\n            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #e6a23c, #f5c97b);\n        }\n        .icon-qa {\n            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1890ff, #69c0ff);\n        }\n        .icon-resources {\n            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #722ed1, #b37feb);\n        }\n        .card-title {\n            font-size: 22px;\n            font-weight: 900;\n            color: #335239;\n        }\n        /* 知识树 */\n        .knowledge-tree {\n            flex: 1;\n            display: flex;\n            flex-direction: column;\n            justify-content: space-between;\n        }\n        .tree-node {\n            display: flex;\n            align-items: center;\n            margin-bottom: 16px;\n            position: relative;\n        }\n        .tree-node::before {\n            content: \'\';\n            position: absolute;\n            left: 12px;\n            top: 24px;\n            width: 2px;\n            height: calc(100% + 16px);\n            background: #c6d6bf;\n            z-index: 1;\n        }\n        .tree-node:last-child::before {\n            display: none;\n        }\n        .node-marker {\n            width: 24px;\n            height: 24px;\n            border-radius: 50%;\n            background: #7da965;\n            display: flex;\n            align-items: center;\n            justify-content: center;\n            color: white;\n            font-size: 12px;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            margin-right: 16px;\n            z-index: 2;\n            position: relative;\n        }\n        .node-content {\n            flex: 1;\n            background: #f8fbf6;\n            border-radius: 12px;\n            padding: 14px 18px;\n            border: 1px solid #e3ece0;\n        }\n        .node-content h4 {\n            font-size: 16px;\n            color: #4d7048;\n            margin-bottom: 6px;\n            font-weight: 900;\n        }\n        .node-content ul {\n            list-style: none;\n            padding-left: 0;\n        }\n        .node-content li {\n            font-size: 13px;\n            color: #607163;\n            line-height: 1.6;\n            margin-bottom: 4px;\n            padding-left: 16px;\n            position: relative;\n        }\n        .node-content li::before {\n            content: \"•\";\n            position: absolute;\n            left: 4px;\n            color: #7da965;\n            font-weight: bold;\n        }\n        /* 注意事项 */\n        .warning-grid {\n            display: grid;\n            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;\n            gap: 16px;\n            margin-top: 10px;\n        }\n        .warning-item {\n            background: #fff9e6;\n            border: 1px solid #f5c97b;\n            border-radius: 14px;\n            padding: 16px;\n            transition: all 0.3s ease;\n        }\n        .warning-item:hover {\n            background: #fff4d1;\n            transform: scale(1.02);\n        }\n        .warning-item h4 {\n            color: #e6a23c;\n            font-size: 15px;\n            margin-bottom: 8px;\n            font-weight: 900;\n        }\n        .warning-item p {\n            font-size: 13px;\n            color: #8a6d3b;\n            line-height: 1.5;\n        }\n        /* 右侧互动区域 */\n        .interaction-section {\n            flex: 1;\n            display: flex;\n            flex-direction: column;\n            gap: 20px;\n        }\n        /* Q&A区域 */\n        .qa-card {\n            flex: 1;\n            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.95);\n            border-radius: 20px;\n            padding: 24px;\n            box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(25,144,255,0.12);\n            border: 1px solid rgba(25,144,255,.15);\n            display: flex;\n            flex-direction: column;\n            position: relative;\n            overflow: hidden;\n        }\n        .qa-content {\n            flex: 1;\n            display: flex;\n            flex-direction: column;\n            justify-content: center;\n            align-items: center;\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 20px 0;\n        }\n        .qa-icon {\n            width: 80px;\n            height: 80px;\n            border-radius: 50%;\n            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1890ff, #69c0ff);\n            display: flex;\n            align-items: center;\n            justify-content: center;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            animation: pulse 2s infinite;\n        }\n        @keyframes pulse {\n            0% { transform: scale(1); }\n            50% { transform: scale(1.05); }\n            100% { transform: scale(1); }\n        }\n        .qa-icon i {\n            font-size: 36px;\n            color: white;\n        }\n        .qa-text {\n            max-width: 80%;\n        }\n        .qa-text h3 {\n            font-size: 20px;\n            color: #1890ff;\n            margin-bottom: 12px;\n            font-weight: 900;\n        }\n        .qa-text p {\n            font-size: 14px;\n            color: #607163;\n            line-height: 1.6;\n            margin-bottom: 16px;\n        }\n        .qa-actions {\n            display: flex;\n            gap: 12px;\n            margin-top: 10px;\n        }\n        .qa-button {\n            padding: 10px 20px;\n            border-radius: 50px;\n            background: #1890ff;\n            color: white;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            border: none;\n            cursor: pointer;\n            transition: all 0.3s ease;\n            display: flex;\n            align-items: center;\n            gap: 8px;\n        }\n        .qa-button:hover {\n            background: #096dd9;\n            transform: translateY(-2px);\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(25,144,255,0.3);\n        }\n        .qa-button.secondary {\n            background: #f0f9eb;\n            color: #52c41a;\n            border: 1px solid #b7eb8f;\n        }\n        .qa-button.secondary:hover {\n            background: #d9f7be;\n        }\n        /* 参考资料区域 */\n        .resources-card {\n            flex: 1;\n            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.95);\n            border-radius: 20px;\n            padding: 24px;\n            box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(114,46,209,0.12);\n            border: 1px solid rgba(114,46,209,.15);\n            display: flex;\n            flex-direction: column;\n        }\n        .resources-content {\n            flex: 1;\n            display: flex;\n            flex-direction: column;\n            gap: 16px;\n        }\n        .resource-category {\n            background: #f9f0ff;\n            border-radius: 12px;\n            padding: 16px;\n            border-left: 4px solid #722ed1;\n        }\n        .resource-category h4 {\n            color: #722ed1;\n            font-size: 16px;\n            margin-bottom: 10px;\n            font-weight: 900;\n            display: flex;\n            align-items: center;\n            gap: 8px;\n        }\n        .resource-category ul {\n            list-style: none;\n            padding-left: 0;\n        }\n        .resource-category li {\n            font-size: 13px;\n            color: #607163;\n            line-height: 1.6;\n            margin-bottom: 6px;\n            padding-left: 20px;\n            position: relative;\n        }\n        .resource-category li::before {\n            content: \"→\";\n            position: absolute;\n            left: 4px;\n            color: #b37feb;\n        }\n        /* 页脚 - 严格保持原样 */\n        .footer {\n            position: absolute;\n            bottom: 20px;\n            left: 0;\n            right: 0;\n            text-align: center;\n            font-size: 14px;\n            color: #7e8e7f;\n            z-index: 30;\n        }\n        .page-number {\n            font-weight: 800;\n            color: #5f7860;\n        }\n        /* 装饰元素 */\n        .decoration {\n            position: absolute;\n            z-index: 1;\n            opacity: 0.1;\n        }\n        .dec-1 {\n            width: 120px;\n            height: 120px;\n            border-radius: 50%;\n            background: #4e874c;\n            top: 120px;\n            right: 60px;\n        }\n        .dec-2 {\n            width: 80px;\n            height: 80px;\n            border-radius: 50%;\n            background: #7da965;\n            bottom: 100px;\n            left: 80px;\n        }\n        .dec-3 {\n            width: 60px;\n            height: 60px;\n            border-radius: 50%;\n            background: #c9d97c;\n            top: 180px;\n            left: 100px;\n        }\n        .dec-4 {\n            width: 100px;\n            height: 100px;\n            border-radius: 30% 70% 70% 30% / 30% 30% 70% 70%;\n            background: #8cb267;\n            bottom: 150px;\n            right: 100px;\n        }\n        /* 响应式调整 */\n        @media (max-width: 1350px) {\n            .page-title h2 {\n                font-size: 36px;\n            }\n            .card-title {\n                font-size: 20px;\n            }\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <div class=\"slide-container\">\n        <div class=\"slide\">\n            <!-- 页眉 - 严格保持原样 -->\n            <div class=\"header\">\n                <div>\n                    <h1>食品药品职业学院 PPT 模板描述文件（字段规范版）</h1>\n                    <p>参照 template.html 的\"单文件、自包含、固定 1280×720、响应式缩放、占位符与规则说明\"写法，在 v3 的子版式拆分基础上，继续把字段命名、选型规则、禁用场景和母版约束标准化，方便后续直接拿来生成新的 PPT。</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"main-tabs\" id=\"mainTabs\">\n                    <button class=\"main-tab\">封面系统</button>\n                    <button class=\"main-tab\">目录系统</button>\n                    <button class=\"main-tab active\">内容系统</button>\n                    <button class=\"main-tab\">数据系统</button>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            <!-- 主要内容区域 -->\n            <div class=\"main-content\">\n                <div class=\"page-title\">\n                    <h2>总结与Q&A</h2>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"content-container\">\n                    <!-- 左侧总结区域 -->\n                    <div class=\"summary-section\">\n                        <!-- 核心知识点 -->\n                        <div class=\"summary-card\">\n                            <div class=\"card-header\">\n                                <div class=\"card-icon icon-knowledge\">\n                                    <i class=\"fas fa-brain\"></i>\n                                </div>\n                                <h3 class=\"card-title\">核心知识点总结</h3>\n                            </div>\n                            <div class=\"knowledge-tree\">\n                                <div class=\"tree-node\">\n                                    <div class=\"node-marker\">P</div>\n                                    <div class=\"node-content\">\n                                        <h4>指针高级应用</h4>\n                                        <ul>\n                                            <li>多级指针与复杂数据结构</li>\n                                            <li','{}',NULL,0,1773720000,1773720000);
